Easy Migrate
===========

Providing very simple migrations that cover both the app and all your plugins.

* Works with timestamp format migrations
* Provides db:migrate and db:down (both should also allow you to pass VERSION=...)
* Currently does not work under Windows


Future Features
===============

* Ability to migrate and demigrate on a per plugin/app basis
* Windows support


